1056
02:03:13,837 --> 02:03:18,344
[SPEAKER_40]: We celebrate them two times in Mexico City, St. Patrick's Day and September 12th.

1057
02:03:19,085 --> 02:03:24,733
[SPEAKER_40]: And so it is appropriate that on our Day of El Grito, and talking about the resistance, I just say that

1058
02:03:25,456 --> 02:03:32,532
[SPEAKER_40]: Mexican-American culture, Latino culture is special to you, but it should be special to every single one of us.

1059
02:03:32,612 --> 02:03:33,214
[SPEAKER_40]: So thank you.

1060
02:03:35,539 --> 02:03:37,423
[SPEAKER_43]: Thank you so much, Councilmember Jurado.

1061
02:03:39,682 --> 02:03:44,695
[SPEAKER_56]: Thank you to La Madrina Councilmember Hernandez for hosting this presentation.

