1071
02:04:47,421 --> 02:04:52,066
[SPEAKER_56]: You're able to make community anywhere that you go with everyone that's around you.

1072
02:04:52,126 --> 02:04:58,754
[SPEAKER_56]: And everyone even on our campaign has a story of when they met you or how they got to know you.

1073
02:04:58,774 --> 02:05:07,245
